name: Puri Agung Inn
address: HF7H+628, Jl. Baledan, Selat, Kec. Selat, Kabupaten Karangasem, Bali 80862, Indonesia
review 1:
Despite the negative reviews on booking platforms, this was a nice pleasant stay.

The owner was friendly and cheerful. Garden was very nice. The rooms showed their age, and could use a little bit more cleanliness.
review 2: Its a beautiful place, beautiful garden, nice water fountains, very friendly staff, delicious breakfast and some cute kittens to pet. Am awesome rice field opposite, much better than sideman rice trek, fire flies in the night there, great and very cheap warungs nearby, what else would a tourist need
review 3: I had a dream when i sleep there. The dream is i got a shot by a big gun. And then i woke up. After i checked out, the material in the bathroom is falling apart. So thats a reason why i got the nightmare. Sound from the material is a gun in my dream. And the place is spooky
